name: Utility Minicards
description: Attach these double-sided minicards to player cards, locations, enemies, etc. whenever there’s a temporary effect on another card that you might otherwise forget. Cards show when you have temporary stat boosts or deductions; remind you when an enemy doesn’t ready at the end of the round; indicate lost actions, customizable configurations, and more.
